    "category": "comparison",
    "list_name": "comparison-and-ease",
    "expression": "AよりBのほうが～",
    "connection": "比较基准 A + より + 被突出项 B + のほうが + 评价；两项择一可用「どちらのほう」",
    "explanation_zh": "「より」标出比较时离开的基准，「ほう」指出评价更偏向的一方。",
    "source_url": "https://guidetojapanese.org/learn/grammar/comparison",
    "license_key": "cc-by-nc-sa-3.0",
    "content_version": "2026-07-15",
    "display_order": 77,
    "published": true,
    "path": "expressions",
    "examples": [
      {
        "ja": "バスより電車のほうが早いです。",
        "zh": "电车比公交车快。",
        "source": "kotonoha-original"
      }
    ],
    "common_mistakes": [
      "「AよりBのほうが速い」中更快的是B；不要受中文“比”字句影响把比较方向读反，也不要漏掉「ほう」后的「が」。"
    ],
    "related_entries": [
      "grammar:tae-kim:i-adjectives",
      "grammar:tae-kim:dake-shika"
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "grammar:tae-kim:yasui-nikui",
