  {
    "id": "grammar:tae-kim:naide-without",
    "source_id": "tae-kim-grammar",
    "source_key": "tae-kim:naide-without",
    "slug": "naide-without",
    "category": "clauses",
    "list_name": "clause-relations",
    "expression": "～ないで",
    "connection": "动词ない形 + で；する→しないで，来る→こないで",
    "explanation_zh": "表示在没有完成前项动作的情况下进行后项，相当于“不……就／没……而……”。",
    "source_url": "https://guidetojapanese.org/learn/grammar/negativeverbs2",
    "license_key": "cc-by-nc-sa-3.0",
    "content_version": "2026-07-15",
    "display_order": 79,
    "published": true,
    "path": "expressions",
    "examples": [
      {
        "ja": "朝ご飯を食べないで学校へ行きました。",
        "zh": "没吃早饭就去学校了。",
        "source": "kotonoha-original"
      }
    ],
    "common_mistakes": [
      "表示伴随状态“没做A而做B”用「ないで」；单纯连接否定或说明原因时常用「なくて」，不要把两者机械互换。"
    ],
    "related_entries": [
      "grammar:tae-kim:verb-negative",
      "grammar:tae-kim:te-combinations"
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "grammar:tae-kim:nagara-while",
    "source_id": "tae-kim-grammar",
    "source_key": "tae-kim:nagara-while",
    "slug": "nagara-while",
    "category": "time",
    "list_name": "clause-relations",
    "expression": "～ながら",
    "connection": "动词连用形 + ながら + 主要动作",
    "explanation_zh": "表示同一主体在进行前项动作的同时进行后项；主要叙述重点通常在后项。",
    "source_url": "https://guidetojapanese.org/learn/grammar/timeactions",
    "license_key": "cc-by-nc-sa-3.0",
    "content_version": "2026-07-15",
    "display_order": 80,
    "published": true,
    "path": "expressions",
    "examples": [
      {
        "ja": "音楽を聞きながら勉強します。",
        "zh": "我一边听音乐一边学习。",
        "source": "kotonoha-original"
      }
    ],
    "common_mistakes": [
      "并行动作原则上共享同一主体；若前后动作由不同的人完成，不能只靠「ながら」连接，应改用「間に」等更明确的结构。"
    ],
    "related_entries": [
      "grammar:tae-kim:te-combinations",
      "grammar:tae-kim:toki-time"
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "grammar:tae-kim:node-reason",
    "source_id": "tae-kim-grammar",
    "source_key": "tae-kim:node-reason",
    "slug": "node-reason",
    "category": "reasoning",
    "list_name": "clause-relations",
    "expression": "～ので",
    "connection": "动词／い形容词普通形 + ので；名词／な形容词 + なので",
    "explanation_zh": "把前项作为后项的原因或背景，语气常比直接主张理由的「から」更说明性、更缓和。",
    "source_url": "https://guidetojapanese.org/learn/grammar/compound",
    "license_key": "cc-by-nc-sa-3.0",
    "content_version": "2026-07-15",
    "display_order": 81,
    "published": true,
    "path": "expressions",
    "examples": [
      {
        "ja": "雨が降っているので、試合は中止です。",
        "zh": "因为正在下雨，比赛取消。",
        "source": "kotonoha-original"
      }
    ],
    "common_mistakes": [
      "名词和な形容词要接「なので」，不能写「雨だので／静かだので」；「ので」给原因，而「のに」表示与预期相反，二者不要因只差一个音而混淆。"
    ],
    "related_entries": [
      "grammar:tae-kim:kara-reason",
      "grammar:tae-kim:noni-contrast"
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "grammar:tae-kim:noni-contrast",
    "source_id": "tae-kim-grammar",
    "source_key": "tae-kim:noni-contrast",
    "slug": "noni-contrast",
    "category": "contrast",
    "list_name": "clause-relations",
    "expression": "～のに",
    "connection": "动词／い形容词普通形 + のに；名词／な形容词 + なのに",
    "explanation_zh": "连接实际结果与前项形成的预期冲突，常带有意外、不满或惋惜。",
    "source_url": "https://guidetojapanese.org/learn/grammar/compound",
    "license_key": "cc-by-nc-sa-3.0",
    "content_version": "2026-07-15",
    "display_order": 82,
    "published": true,
    "path": "expressions",
    "examples": [
      {
        "ja": "電池を替えたのに、時計が動きません。",
        "zh": "明明换了电池，钟却不走。",
        "source": "kotonoha-original"
      }
    ],
    "common_mistakes": [
      "「のに」不是原因连接词：若后项是前项的正常结果应用「ので」；句末单独用「のに」还可能留下“明明……”的遗憾语气。"
    ],
    "related_entries": [
      "grammar:tae-kim:node-reason",
      "grammar:tae-kim:kara-reason"
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "grammar:tae-kim:toki-time",
    "source_id": "tae-kim-grammar",
