    "slug": "mae-ni-before",
    "category": "time",
    "list_name": "time-and-deadlines",
    "expression": "～前に",
    "connection": "动词辞书形 + 前に；名词 + の前に",
    "explanation_zh": "表示后项发生在前项动作或某个时间点之前。",
    "source_url": "https://guidetojapanese.org/learn/complete/verb_sequences",
    "license_key": "cc-by-nc-sa-3.0",
    "content_version": "2026-07-15",
    "display_order": 84,
    "published": true,
    "path": "expressions",
    "examples": [
      {
        "ja": "出かける前に、窓を閉めました。",
        "zh": "出门前，我关了窗户。",
        "source": "kotonoha-original"
      }
    ],
    "common_mistakes": [
      "即使后项发生在过去，「前に」前通常仍用辞书形表示尚未发生的动作；应说「出かける前に」，不是「出かけた前に」。"
    ],
    "related_entries": [
      "grammar:tae-kim:toki-time",
      "grammar:tae-kim:ato-de-after"
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "grammar:tae-kim:ato-de-after",
