    "category": "time",
    "list_name": "time-and-deadlines",
    "expression": "～後で",
    "connection": "动词た形 + 後で；名词 + の後で",
    "explanation_zh": "明确表示前项完成之后再发生后项，适合交代动作顺序。",
    "source_url": "https://guidetojapanese.org/learn/complete/verb_sequences",
    "license_key": "cc-by-nc-sa-3.0",
    "content_version": "2026-07-15",
    "display_order": 85,
    "published": true,
    "path": "expressions",
    "examples": [
      {
        "ja": "食事をした後で、散歩しましょう。",
        "zh": "吃完饭后去散步吧。",
        "source": "kotonoha-original"
      }
    ],
    "common_mistakes": [
      "动词在「後で」前要用た形，因为作为基准的动作已完成；不能照搬「前に」的连接写成「食事をする後で」。"
